<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>About Us - Book Catalog</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/styles.css">
</head>
<body>
    <!-- Header -->
    <%- include('../partials/header-before-login') %>

    <!-- Main Content -->
    <main class="centered-container">
        <div class="about-container">
            <h1>About Us</h1>

            <!-- Section: Our Mission -->
            <section class="about-section">
                <h2><i class="fas fa-bullseye"></i> Our Mission</h2>
                <p>
                    At Book Catalog, our mission is to provide readers with access to the best collection of books from around the world. We believe that books are a gateway to knowledge, imagination, and personal growth.
                </p>
            </section>

            <!-- Section: Who We Are -->
            <section class="about-section">
                <h2><i class="fas fa-users"></i> Who We Are</h2>
                <p>
                    Founded in 2023, Book Catalog started as a small project by a group of book enthusiasts who wanted to create a platform where people could easily discover and explore books. Today, we have grown into a community-driven platform loved by readers worldwide.
                </p>
            </section>

            <!-- Section: Why Choose Us? -->
            <section class="about-section">
                <h2><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> Why Choose Us?</h2>
                <ul class="about-list">
                    <li><i class="fas fa-book"></i> Wide selection of books across genres</li>
                    <li><i class="fas fa-search"></i> User-friendly interface for easy navigation</li>
                    <li><i class="fas fa-sync-alt"></i> Regular updates with new releases</li>
                    <li><i class="fas fa-users"></i> A passionate community of readers and authors</li>
                </ul>
            </section>
        </div>
    </main>

    <!-- Footer -->
    <%- include('../partials/footer') %>
</body>
</html>